Available Tools: purchase_item | get_item_info | check_availability
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "slot_id": "string", "quantity": number }
Response Schema: { "slot_id": "string", "item_name": "string", "price": number, "status": "string" }
---
Question: Do you have any Sprite in slot F2?
Call: { "func_call": "check_availability", "slot_id": "F2", "quantity": 1 }
Response: { "slot_id": "F2", "item_name": "Sprite Lemon-Lime", "price": 1.5, "status": "in_stock" }

Question: Check if the doritos in slot G4 are available.
Call: { "func_call": "check_availability", "slot_id": "G4", "quantity": 1 }
Response: { "slot_id": "G4", "item_name": "Doritos Nacho Cheese", "price": 1.75, "status": "low_stock" }

Question: Can I purchase a KitKat from slot H1 right now?
